      "updated": 1783361284287,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Distributed application - applications that work together across a network.\nDCOM, RDP, COM+\n\n\"Universal Data Access\" - XML\n    - \"Embrace, Extend, Extinguish\" \n\n\nApplication Layer Protocol (HTTP), SOAP (Simple object access protocol) W3C Soap \n\"XML Web Services\", \"WCF\" (Windows Communication Foundation)\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Distributed application - applications that work together across a network.\nDCOM, RDP, COM+\n\n\"Universal Data Access\" - XML\n    - \"Embrace, Extend, Extinguish\" \n\n\nApplication Layer Protocol (HTTP), SOAP (Simple object access protocol) W3C Soap \n\"XML Web Services\", \"WCF\" (Windows Communication Foundation)\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
